{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/ClickButtons.gif?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Boba Teashop</strong> is a cozy horror game where you own and manage a boba tea shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare boba teas, serve customers, and expand your menu to attract more patrons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/TBT_Divider_ManageABobaShop.png?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/RisaFace-optimize.gif?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You play as Risa, a woman in her 30s who is tired of corporate life and has decided to chase her dream of opening a boba tea shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/TBT_Divider_ServeCustomers.png?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/Customerwalksin-optimize.gif?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a boba tea shop owner, you will encounter a variety of customers.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your job is to greet them with a smile and take their orders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/TBT_Divider_MakeDeliciousBoba.png?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/MakingDrinks-optimize.gif?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Making boba tea is simple.\u00a0The ingredients are just milk tea and boba.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Seal the cup with a lid and serve it with a straw for sipping and enjoying the boba pearls.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/TroublesomeCustomers_2_Optimize.gif?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But sometimes, you'll encounter demanding customers with special requests or those who leave a mess in your shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the proud owner of a boba tea shop, there's nothing you can't handle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/TBT_Divider_Terror-effect2.gif?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/Terror_optimized.gif?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While serving customers and managing your boba tea shop, you start seeing visions and hearing things.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Is it all in your head, or is something haunting the place?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is\u00a0psychological horror game that builds tension through eerie atmosphere, unsettling events, and moments of intense scare when you least expect them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay:</strong> A simple yet engaging loop where you take orders from customers, prepare their drinks, and serve them with a smile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>VHS Aesthetics:</strong> Experience the game through a creepy VHS filter that adds a nostalgic and eerie atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story:</strong> Uncover Risa's journey and personal growth as she pursues her dream of becoming a successful boba tea shop owner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739174632","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739174632","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/659bc69eee69a564bba3b795b9cbd83e995149d6/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739174632","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/659bc69eee69a564bba3b795b9cbd83e995149d6/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739174632","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/ClickButtons.gif?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Boba Teashop</strong> is a cozy horror game where you own and manage a boba tea shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare boba teas, serve customers, and expand your menu to attract more patrons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/TBT_Divider_ManageABobaShop.png?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/RisaFace-optimize.gif?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">