_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/TBT_Divider_Terror-effect2.gif?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/extras/Terror_optimized.gif?t=1739174632\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While serving customers and managing your boba tea shop, you start seeing visions and hearing things.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Is it all in your head, or is something haunting the place?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is\u00a0psychological horror game that builds tension through eerie atmosphere, unsettling events, and moments of intense scare when you least expect them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay:</strong> A simple yet engaging loop where you take orders from customers, prepare their drinks, and serve them with a smile.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>VHS Aesthetics:</strong> Experience the game through a creepy VHS filter that adds a nostalgic and eerie atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story:</strong> Uncover Risa's journey and personal growth as she pursues her dream of becoming a successful boba tea shop owner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["Mike Ten"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3461920/header.jpg?t=1739174632","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257088639,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257088639/movie480.mp4?t=1737128872","max":"http://video.ak